big-integer.description: Store whole numbers from -(2${startSup}53${endSup}-1) to 2${startSup}53${endSup}-1. Use this field type when using numbers that are outside of the supported integer field range.
big-integer.title: Big Integer

date.description: Store values with date and time.
date.title: Date

date-only.description: Store date values with no time values.
date-only.title: Date Only

global-id.description: Store a 36 character string consisting of letters and numbers used to uniquely identify a feature.
global-id.title: GlobalID

guid.description: Store a 36 character string consisting of letters and numbers. A Globally Unique Identifier, or GUID, is frequently used to manage relationships between features.
guid.title: GUID

string.description: Store a set of alphanumeric characters
string.title: String

time-only.description: Store time values with no date values.
time-only.title: Time Only

timestamp-offset.description: Store values indicating the date, time, and offset from Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
timestamp-offset.title: Timestamp Offset
